<p>
Greg Ashton
<a href="http://arxiv.org/abs/1111.1138">  M. Bernhardt, W. Becker, T. Prinz, F. Breithuth, U. Walter - <i> Autonomous Spacecraft Navigation Based on Pulsar Timing Information</i> </a>
